name: Dissolving Painting 7 - Wanderer
description:
On the threshold of the unknown, the cold wind, and the endless sky. I cherish, those who wander, in their search for new paths. 
This is my interpretation of Wanderer above the Sea of Fog, one of the masterpieces of Romanticism by the German Romantic artist Caspar David Friedrich. 
By RubenFro - Twitter: @Ruben_Fro
